"Obscures:\n"
"This unit darkens the surrounding area, making chaotic units fight better, "
"and lawful units fight worse.\n"
"\n"
"Any units adjacent to this unit will fight as if it were dusk when it is "
"day, and as if it were night when it is dusk."
msgstr ""
"Obscurcissement :\n"
"Cette unité obscurcit son voisinage, permettant aux unité chaotiques de "
"mieux combattre tandis que les normales sont désavantagées.\n"
"\n"
"Toute unité voisine combattra comme si c'était le crépuscule quand il fait "
"jour, et comme si c'était la nuit au crépuscule."

