msgid ""
"Inside of the burned village of Ruen, Gawen's soldiers found massacred "
"bodies of men, women and children. No one was unmoved by the terrible sight. "
"Looking at their faces, Gawen sadly realized that the Orcs would not expect "
"any mercy in this battle and no prisoners would be taken."
msgstr ""
"Dans le village dévasté de Ruen, les soldats de Gawen trouvèrent les corps "
"massacrés d'hommes, de femmes et d'enfants. Personne ne put rester "
"indifférent devant ce terrible spectacle. En voyant leurs visages, Gawen "
"pensa tristement qu'il ne fallait pas attendre de pitié des orcs durant "
"cette bataille et qu'on n'y ferait pas de prisonniers."

