#. [scenario]: id=11_Council_in_Freetown
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:3
msgid "Council in Freetown"
msgstr "Conseil à Freetown"

#. [part]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The day was bright when Gawen Hagarthen entered the forests of Raedwood. "
"There, inside the very heart of the forest, lay the city of Freetown, "
"founded by refugees from lands under the heavy Akladian yoke. Life was not "
"easy here, food was scarce, and yet smiles were often seen on the faces of "
"men and women."
msgstr ""
"Le jour était déjà levé quand Gawen Hagarthen entra dans les forêts de "
"Raedwood. Là, au coeur de la forêt, se trouvait la cité de Freetown, fondée "
"par les réfugiés des territoires sous le joug des Akladiens. La vie n'y "
"était pas facile, la nourriture était rare, et pourtant, les hommes et les "
"femmes souriaient souvent."

#. [part]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Karen said she could smell the freedom in the air here. Gawen smelled "
"nothing out of the ordinary, though... only the scent of meats being roasted "
"over an open flame. 'Perhaps it is not given to royalty to smell freedom,' "
"he thought. Messengers waited for Ruvio, asking him to come to the meeting "
"of the Freetown leaders. "
msgstr ""
"Karen dit qu'elle pouvait sentir le parfum de la liberté dans l'air à cet "
"endroit. Gawen ne sentait rien d'extraordinaire... sauf l'odeur des viandes "
"cuites à la broche. « Peut-être n'est-il pas donné aux gens de sang royal de "
"sentir ce parfum », se dit-il. Des messagers attendaient Ruvio, pour lui "
"demander d'aller à la réunion des chefs de Freetown."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:202
msgid "Welcome back to Freetown, Ruvio. You are just in time for our meeting."
msgstr ""
"Heureux de te revoir à Freetown, Ruvio. Tu arrives juste à temps pour la "
"réunion."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:203
msgid ""
"We also welcome your daughter. Karen, I would order you to leave this "
"meeting and go to your mother..."
msgstr ""
"Que votre fille soit aussi la bienvenue. Karen, je voudrais que tu quittes "
"cette réunion et ailles rejoindre ta mère..."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:204
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "... but you know that you would only waste your breath."
msgid "...but you know that you would only waste your breath."
msgstr "... mais tu sais que tu ne ferais que gaspiller ta salive."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:205
msgid ""
"We've heard that you have battled and defeated both Akladians and Outlaws. "
"Accept our congratulations, Ruvio. But who is this young man, your companion?"
msgstr ""
"Nous avons appris que tu avais vaincu les Akladiens et les hors-la-loi. "
"Accepte nos félicitations, Ruvio. Mais qui est ce jeune homme, ton "
"compagnon ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:206
msgid ""
"I participated in the battles you have mentioned, but someone else should be "
"credited for the victory. We were commanded by this young man."
msgstr ""
"J'ai bien participé aux batailles que tu mentionnes, mais un autre devrait "
"recevoir le mérite de la victoire. C'est ce jeune homme qui nous commandait."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:207
msgid "And his name is...?"
msgstr "Et son nom est… ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:208
msgid "Gaumhaldric."
msgstr "Gaumhaldric."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:209
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "(grumbling) I hate you."
msgid "(<i>grumbling</i>) I hate you."
msgstr "(grognement) Je la hais."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:210
msgid ""
"But now, he must leave. We have very important and secret things to talk "
"upon."
msgstr ""
"Mais maintenant, il doit partir. Nous devons discuter de sujets très "
"importants et très secrets."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:211
msgid "He has my full trust. He stays."
msgstr "J'ai pleinement confiance en lui. Il reste."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:212
msgid ""
"So be it. Let's greet our honorable guest, Mithrandil of the northern Elves. "
"He has made a long journey here and he bears important news."
msgstr ""
"Entendu. Maintenant, accueillons notre honorable invité, Mithrandil des "
"elfes du nord. Il a fait un long voyage jusqu'ici et est porteur de "
"nouvelles importantes."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:213
msgid ""
"My respect and best wishes for everyone in this free city. I hope you will "
"forgive me for dispensing with the formalities of a long traditional speech. "
"The news I bring here is simple, and terrifying. The Orcish army has marched "
"unnoticed and unopposed into the very heart of Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"Mes respects et meilleurs voeux à tous ceux de cette cité libre. J'espère "
"que vous me pardonnerez de dispenser des formalités traditionnelles. Les "
"nouvelles que j'apporte sont simples et terrifiantes. L'armée des orcs est "
"arrivée inaperçue et sans résistance jusqu'au coeur de Wesnoth."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:214
msgid ""
"No! That impossible! How that could possibly happened? They would have had "
"to cross through the free realms of the north, and..."
msgstr ""
"Non ! C'est impossible. Comment l'auraient-ils fait. Ils leur fallait "
"traverser les royaumes libres du nord, et..."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:215
msgid ""
"Mithrandil speaks the truth, Huon. You have not seen the reports I've gotten."
msgstr ""
"Mithrandil dit la vérité, Huon. Tu n'as pas vu les rapports que j'ai reçu."

#. [event]
#. presumably the "queen whose name I will not utter" is Asheviere:
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:217
msgid ""
"They indeed crossed the free realms of the north. The relations among humans "
"are none of my business. Also, I will pretend that I have not noticed that "
"you have called me a liar. The Orcish army has appeared in Wesnoth, bringing "
"back dark memories of the queen whose name I will not utter."
msgstr ""
"Ils ont effectivement traversé les royaumes libres du nord. Je ne me soucie "
"pas des relations entre humains. Aussi je vais faire semblant de n'avoir pas "
"remarqué que vous m'avez traité de menteur. L'armée orc est apparue dans "
"Wesnoth, rappelant les horribles souvenirs d'une certaine reine dont je ne "
"prononcerai pas le nom."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:218
msgid ""
"According to what we have gathered, their presence is due to internal strife "
"amongst the Akladians. If Akladians are slaughtering each other, even if "
"with Orcish help, why should free people be disturbed by that?"
msgstr ""
"D'après ce que nous savons, c'est un conflit interne entre Akladiens. Si les "
"Akladiens se massacrent entre eux et même si les orcs les aident, je ne vois "
"pas pourquoi les peuples libres doivent s'en préoccuper ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:219
msgid ""
"We elves believe that this is more than just an Orcish invasion and quarrels "
"between Akladians. Something greater, something evil, is hiding behind this. "
"What it is, we do not know. I came here to warn you, to help you, and ask "
"for your help. We need you to find out the real reason the Orcish army is "
"here. We also need to discover who is hiding behind the invasion. We have "
"our suspicions, but we want to be sure."
msgstr ""
"Nous, les elfes, pensons que ceci est plus qu'une invasion orc et des "
"querelles internes aux Akladiens. Quelque chose de plus grand, de plus "
"maléfique est derrière tout ça. Nous ne savons pas encore quoi exactement. "
"Je suis venu ici pour vous prévenir, vous aider et vous demander de l'aide. "
"Trouvons les vraies raisons de la présence de cette armée orc. Qui se cache "
"derrière cette invasion. Nous avons certes une idée, mais il faut en être "
"sûr."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:220
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We respect wisdom of the Elves, and we will fulfill your request. We will "
#| "send two armies to catch Orcish leaders and investigate them. One will be "
#| "led by Ruvio, second by Huon. Agreed?"
msgid ""
"We respect the wisdom of the Elves, and we will fulfill your request. We "
"will send two armies to catch Orcish leaders and investigate them. One will "
"be led by Ruvio, second by Huon. Agreed?"
msgstr ""
"Nous respectons la sagesse des elfes et nous répondrons à votre demande. "
"Nous enverrons deux armées pour attraper les chefs orcs et les interroger. "
"L'une sera dirigée par Ruvio et l'autre par Huon. D'accord ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:221
msgid ""
"I must insist on one slight change, Gwidle. My army will be led by this "
"young man ... Gaumhaldric."
msgstr ""
"Je dois demander un léger changement, Gwidle. Mon armée sera conduite par "
"ce... Gaumhaldric."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:222
msgid ""
"I will join Huon with part of my escort, I will gave the rest of them to "
"Ruv... er... to Gah - uhm - haldreeck. My finest archer, my best captain, "
"two fighters and another archer. In addition, would you prefer to get a "
"Scout or Shaman?"
msgstr ""
"Je me joindrai à Huon avec une partie de mon escorte, le reste ira avec "
"Ruv... er... avec Gah — hum — Haldreeck. Mon meilleur archer, mon meilleur "
"capitaine, deux combattants et un autre archer. De plus, préféreriez-vous un "
"éclaireur ou une chamane ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gawen Hagarthen
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:226
msgid "I think that..."
msgstr "Je pense que..."

#. [option]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/11_Council_in_Freetown.cfg:228
msgid "A Shaman would be great."
msgstr "Une chamane serait très utile."

