#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Vattin, the capital of our kingdom, is just a few days from here. How do you "
"feel, my son? "
msgstr ""
"Vattin, la capitale de notre royaume, n'est qu'à quelques jours d'ici. Mon "
"fils, comment te sens-tu ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Much better. That medic did a commendable job. I wish to thank him at some "
"time in future."
msgstr ""
"Beaucoup mieux. Ce médecin était vraiment bon. J'espère pouvoir le remercier "
"un jour ou l'autre."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:261
msgid "I'm afraid... that may be... impossible. What about your memory?"
msgstr ""
"J'ai peur... que cela ne soit... impossible. Et comment va ta mémoire ?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:262
msgid ""
"I think... sometimes I think I remember something, but then it passes. I "
"remember a dark-haired woman. She is lying on a bed, sweating, pain in her "
"beautiful green eyes. I don't know who she is, but it makes me want to weep "
"every time I think about it. I think... I think I loved her."
msgstr ""
"Je pense... Parfois, je pense que je me souviens de quelque chose, mais "
"alors ça repart aussitôt. Je me souviens d'une femme aux cheveux sombres. "
"Elle est couchée sur un lit, elle transpire. Il y a de la souffrance dans "
"ses beaux yeux verts. Je ne sais pas qui elle est, mais cela me donne envie "
"de pleurer à chaque fois que j'y pense. Je crois que je l'aimais beaucoup."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:263
msgid ""
"That could be your true mother, my lord. She was poisoned when you were "
"still young."
msgstr ""
"Il pourrait s'agir de votre vraie mère, Monseigneur. Elle a été empoisonnée "
"quand vous étiez encore enfant."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:264
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| " I've sent an envoy to Gaeltin Hyer, a city which lies along our way, to "
#| "prepare rooms for us. I think, my lord, you might want to get some rest "
#| "before continuing our journey."
msgid ""
"...anyways, I've sent an envoy to Gaeltin Hyer, a city which lies along our "
"way, to prepare rooms for us. I think, my lord, you might want to get some "
"rest before continuing our journey."
msgstr ""
"J'ai envoyé un messager à Gaeltin Hyer, une ville qui est sur notre chemin, "
"pour qu'ils préparent des chambres pour nous. Je crois, Monseigneur, que "
"vous aimeriez prendre du repos avant de continuer le voyage."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Noble lords, with your permission... my lord, Raul O Gaeltin sent me here "
"with a message. I beg for your forgiveness, remember I am just a messenger."
msgstr ""
"Nobles seigneurs, avec votre permission. Mon seigneur, Raul O Gaeltin "
"m'envoie avec un message. Je vous demande de me pardonner d'avance, souvenez-"
"vous que je ne suis qu'un messager."

#. [event]
#. Lorin speaking
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:282
msgid "Speak."
msgstr "Parlez."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:283
msgid ""
"These are the words of my lord; I was given a strict charge to repeat them "
"exactly: 'Gaeltin's gates will never be opened for mixling bastards nor for "
"the king's whores.' He also sends this..."
msgstr ""
"Voici ce que dit mon seigneur, il m'a chargé de répèter son message mot pour "
"mot : les portes de Gaeltin ne s'ouvriront jamais ni pour les bâtards, ni "
"pour les putains du roi. Il vous envoie également ceci..."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:284
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "You received 2 pieces of gold"
msgid "You received 2 pieces of gold."
msgstr "Vous recevez 2 pièces d'or."

#. [event]
#. this is a continuation of the Messenger's previous message:
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:290
msgid ""
"'...for you to start a new life.' This is what I was commanded to say. May I "
"live - I mean - leave?"
msgstr ""
"...pour permettre de commencer une nouvelle vie. C'est tout ce que je devais "
"dire. Puis-je partir ?"

#. [event]
#. Reme speaking
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:292
msgid ""
"We have a message for your lord too. Tell him we will bring him the message "
"personally and he will have a lot of time to comprehend it fully. You may "
"leave now."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons aussi un message pour ton seigneur. Dis-lui que nous le lui "
"apporterons personnellement et qu'il aura tout le temps de le comprendre "
"entièrement. Tu peux partir, maintenant."

#. [event]
#. Lorin speaking
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:314
msgid ""
"I guess we will have to fight our way into Vattin. Gawen, many Akladians "
"live nearby. They will fight for you. They are inexperienced but they are "
"eager to show their loyalty. Let's use them."
msgstr ""
"Je suppose que nous allons devoir nous ouvrir de force un chemin vers "
"Vattin. Gawen, beaucoup d'Akladiens vivent par ici. Ils se battront pour "
"toi. Ils sont inexpérimentés, mais anxieux de prouver leur loyauté. "
"Utilisons-les."

#. [event]
#. Reme speaking
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Hmm, after some thought perhaps it is for the best that Raul is trying to "
"oppose us. It's an occasion for you to exercise a little."
msgstr ""
"Hum, en y réfléchissant, c'est peut-être une bonne chose que ce Raul essaie "
"de nous arrêter. C'est une occasion de vous entraîner un peu."

#. [event]
#. no hints for NIGHTMARE difficulty:
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:319
msgid "Go and attack however you see fit; I highly doubt you need my advice."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. all other difficulties; we can have hints on those:
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Go and take the villages to earn more gold. Recruit as many Clansmen as you "
"can. Many of them will probably die, but the survivors may become good "
"fighters. Do not forget to recall our veteran soldiers, too. Be careful; do "
"not needlessly hurry. To cure wounded units you may use wisemen or villages."
msgstr ""
"Allez prendre les villages pour récupérer de l'or. Recrutez autant de "
"membres du clan que vous le pouvez. La plupart mourront probablement, mais "
"les survivants peuvent devenir de bons combattants. N'oubliez pas non plus "
"de rappeler nos soldats vétérans. Soyez prudent, ne vous hâtez pas sans "
"nécessité. Vous pouvez utiliser les sages ou les villages pour soigner les "
"unités blessées."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:329
msgid "Reach the northern signpost with Gawen Hagarthen OR"
msgstr "Atteignez le panneau indicateur au nord avec Gawen OU"

